question: Within a radius of 180 kilometers, where can I find  a restaurant from the View Lounge, San Francisco, CA towards Salesforce Park Cable Car, San Francisco, CA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.404326 37.785414)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.396632 37.790201)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.404326 37.785414)',4326)::geography, 180000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.404326 37.785414)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
